<<declare $npc_Lisa = "Lisa">>

// ✅ DIALOGUE BLOCK (Target Language with IDs)
{$npc_Lisa}: 안녕하세요! 잘 지내시나요? #line:l0_sample_001
    -> 네, 잘 지내요. 감사합니다! #line:l0_sample_002
        Player: 네, 잘 지내요. 감사합니다! #line:l0_sample_003
        {$npc_Lisa}: 듣던 중 반가운 소리네요. #line:l0_sample_004
    -> 별로 좋지 않아요. #line:l0_sample_005
        Player: 별로 좋지 않아요. #line:l0_sample_006
        {$npc_Lisa}: 저런, 유감이네요. #line:l0_sample_007
===

// REFERENCE BLOCK (MIRROR)
// Exact match to V4 style: No title header, functioning as unparsed metadata
Lisa: Hello! How are you doing? #line:l0_sample_001
    -> Yes, I am doing well. Thank you! #line:l0_sample_002
        Player: Yes, I am doing well. Thank you! #line:l0_sample_003
        Lisa: That is good to hear. #line:l0_sample_004
    -> Not so good. #line:l0_sample_005
        Player: Not so good. #line:l0_sample_006
        Lisa: Oh, I am sorry. #line:l0_sample_007
